# Game Features

## Snake

Features:

вЂў Walls ON/OFF
вЂў Snake skins
вЂў Background themes
вЂў Multiple fruits
вЂў Clean GUI

Fruit scoring example:

Apple = 1
Banana = 2
Cherry = 5
Golden Apple = 10

---

## Tic Tac Toe

Features:

вЂў Clean UI
вЂў PvP
вЂў PvE
вЂў 3 AI difficulties
вЂў Win line animation
вЂў Super Tic Tac Toe mode

AI levels:

Easy вЂ“ random
Medium вЂ“ block wins
Hard вЂ“ minimax

---

## Memory Match

Emoji card game.

Difficulties:

Easy = 4x4
Medium = 6x6
Hard = 8x8

Extras:

вЂў timer
вЂў move counter
вЂў best score

---

